      <h1 class="hero-heading">Design, mostly.<br /><em>Opinions, always</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">Been doing this since 2016. Started with small freelance projects, ended up at startups and apps with tens of millions of users. Still enjoy it.</p>
